{
  "events": [
    {
      "offset_seconds": 0,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "description": "Video recording starts showing a split view of a student named Iyonna and a tutor named Riona Duncan."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 2,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Hey Iyonna, how's it going?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 6,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "speaker_name": "Iyonna"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 8,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "description": "Student starts screen sharing. Khan Academy window becomes visible.",
      "details": "Browser window showing 'Patterns with numbers' exercise."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 10,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Awesome. Uh-huh. All right.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 13,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "move",
      "x": 300,
      "y": 300,
      "details": "Cursor moves slightly on the left side of the screen."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 14,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So, I just wanted to check in on your goals real quick. Um, we don't have to set anything right now.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 21,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 6,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "But um, currently you've got a target of 30 minutes for the next week...",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 28,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, and two skills to be... four skills, sorry, to be updated.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 31,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Sound good?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 33,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "speaker_name": "Iyonna"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 35,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "All right. Perfect.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 38,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "The following pattern starts with 5 and uses the rule multiply the previous term by 3.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 44,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "hover",
      "target_desc": "number 5 in text",
      "details": "Cursor hovers over the number 5 in the question text."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 47,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "action": "hover",
      "target_desc": "rule text",
      "details": "Cursor hovers over 'multiply the previous term by 3'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 53,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "action": "hover",
      "target_desc": "number sequence",
      "details": "Cursor moves along the sequence '5, 15, 45, 135, 405'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 58,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So, how are you feeling about this kind of question?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 63,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "I don't know, it's confusing.",
      "speaker_name": "Iyonna"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 66,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 69,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "All right.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 114,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 6,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So one way that I would look at this is I would just try and find cases that um...",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 120,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "mean that the answer couldn't be true.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 124,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Cause if it's not true then I can move on to the next one.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 150,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So...",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 151,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 7,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "for this, I would um, look through and figure out what can... might not be true.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 160,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 51,
      "description": "Student stares at the screen without moving the cursor; Tutor waits."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 211,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 5,
      "description": "Screen goes black, participant names 'iyonna' and 'Riona Duncan' appear on black background. Connection interruption."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 216,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "View changes to Tutor's video only."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 221,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "All right, I think I glitched out. Can you see or hear me?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 241,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "All right, I'll be back.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 246,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Black screen with names appears again."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 247,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Video returns to gallery view. A new student is visible, labeled 'Dazjah'."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 251,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Hey Dazjah, how's it going?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 254,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "[inaudible]",
      "speaker_name": "Dazjah"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 254,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Student makes an 'ok' hand sign."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 257,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Awesome. Can you share your screen with me so I know what you're working on?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 259,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 63,
      "description": "Waiting for screen share. Video stays on gallery view."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 322,
      "event_type": "view_change",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Screen share starts showing Khan Academy."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 327,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "You're the best.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 329,
      "event_type": "mouse",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "action": "click",
      "target_desc": "Khanmigo chat close button",
      "x": 880,
      "y": 120,
      "details": "Student clicks the X to close the Khanmigo chat window."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 352,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 6,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So, the first step I would take when I was trying to solve this problem would be to substitute in what I know r is and what I know s is.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 420,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So I would rewrite this as um, 6 times 1/4 plus 14 times 1/4.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 439,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Also just as a check in on your goals, given I have them up, um...",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 445,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Just so you know, you are killing both of them.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 450,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 507,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "In terms of your goal for time put in, you said you'd do 20 minutes, you did 26... 31.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 514,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 7,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So the recommendation is to do 26 um, minutes as your new goal to put it a little higher cause you went so far past it.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 521,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Thumbs up? Perfect. All right.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 522,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Student gives a double thumbs up in the video feed."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 524,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I will set that for you.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 530,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 6,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, and then you did 12 skills, so the highest this goes is 5.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 536,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Um, so the recommendation is to keep it up there at 5.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 541,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Sound decent?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 544,
      "event_type": "system",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "description": "Student gestures with a salute/peace sign."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 545,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Perfect. Awesome. Great work with that.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 553,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 116,
      "description": "Silence. Student looks at the screen, seemingly working on the math problem mentally or on paper. Cursor does not move."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 749,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "You might have the answer? All right.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 751,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "You want to run it by me first before you put it in? Or do you want to just check it by yourself?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 812,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Want to check it? Perfect, that's what I'm here for.",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 814,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So what answer did you get?",
      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 816,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 118,
      "description": "Student continues to look at screen/keyboard area. No audio response or screen interaction captured."
    }
  ]
}

{
  "events": [
    {
      "offset_seconds": 0,
      "event_type": "inactivity",
      "duration_seconds": 52,

    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 52,

      "duration_seconds": 0.5,

    {

    },

      "speaker_name": "Riona Duncan"

    {

      "event_type": "keyboard",

    {
      "offset_seconds": 257,
      "event_type": "view_change",

      "description": "Screen share resumes",
      "details": "View switches back to the student's screen on Quiz 1, Question 1."
    },
    {
      "offset_seconds": 302,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 11,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Alright, I'm back, just to hang out. Um, as I said, feel free to let me know if you have any questions, want to run anything by me. Otherwise, I'll just be here.",
